                COMMON JOB TASKS
            </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
            <h2 class="contentH2">
                What are common job tasks for individuals working in the Medical Lab Assistant / Technician field?
            </h2>
            <p class="contentp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp; Participate as an important member of the laboratory team.
                <br /><hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp; Provide patient reception and documentation.
                <br /><hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp;Use correct techniques to safely collect blood specimens.
                <br /><hr class="hrp">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog blueGoldBorderSM f15"></span>&nbsp; Appropriately handle and distribute specimens to be analyzed by other members of the laboratory team 
